testsweeper
------------------------------------------
TestSweeper is a C++ testing framework for parameter sweeps. It handles parsing
command line options, iterating over the test space, and printing results. This
simplifies test functions by allowing them to concentrate on setting up and
solving one problem at a time.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.3-1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libgomp1-12.4.0-3
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  libtestsweeper-devel-2025.05.28-1bl1
  libtestsweeper0-2025.05.28-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.4.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/icl-utk-edu/testsweeper

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/icl-utk-edu/testsweeper/archive/refs/tags/v2025.05.28.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack testsweeper-2025.05.28-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./testsweeper-2025.05.28-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/testsweeper-2025.05.28-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/testsweeper-2025.05.28-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtestsweeper0-2025.05.28-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtestsweeper-devel-2025.05.28-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(testsweeper)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/testsweeper.README
  /usr/share/doc/testsweeper/CHANGELOG.md
  /usr/share/doc/testsweeper/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/testsweeper/README.md

(libtestsweeper0)
  /usr/bin/cygtestsweeper-0.dll

(libtestsweeper-devel)
  /usr/include/testsweeper.hh
  /usr/lib/cmake/testsweeper/testsweeperConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/testsweeper/testsweeperConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/testsweeper/testsweeperTargets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/testsweeper/testsweeperTargets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libtestsweeper.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/testsweeper.pc

